*TITR
First vesrion of the LGC file Single component
*OLOC 							%OLOC for now, in case of MAD-X, could be *RS2K
*PREC 6
*COVAR
*INSTR
*HLSR HL_SNSR_1 0.02 0 0  		%Precisions used from power point. Name of the standard instrument?
*INCL INCL_SNSR_1   63    0   0 0  0  	%What is your inclinometer precision? Name of the standard instrument?
*EDM FSI_SNSR_1 CORNERCUBE 0 0 0	%FSI as distance measurement
CORNERCUBE .3 0 0 0 0 0 0 0

*CALA
A-TAP.GROUNDREF 0	-1	0
B-TAP.GROUNDREF 0	-1	0
TAP.A.LONGIREF 	0 	-1 	2.4
TAP.L.LONGIREF 	0 	11 	2.4

*DSPT  TAP.A.LONGIREF   FSI_SNSR_1 %observation is a 3D distance between two points. OK with that? do you need an orientation too?
TAP.A.LONGI		2	%MEAS
*DSPT  TAP.L.LONGIREF   FSI_SNSR_1
TAP.L.LONGI 	2	%MEAS

*DVER 0.010							%could be a dist also.  Precision?
A-TAP.GROUNDREF  A-TAP.REF	2	%MEAS
B-TAP.GROUNDREF	 B-TAP.REF	2	%MEAS

*ECWS  HL_SNSR_1  0.001  WSID    WaterNetwork1    %Water network name?
A-TAP.HLS1	0.0295	ID 1	%MEAS
A-TAP.HLS2	0.0295	ID 36	%MEAS
B-TAP.HLS1	0.0295	ID 96	%MEAS
B-TAP.HLS2	0.0295	ID 1000	%MEAS
TAP.A.HLS	0.0295		%MEAS
TAP.L.HLS	0.0295		%MEAS
TAP.Q.HLS	0.0295		%MEAS
TAP.D.HLS	0.0295		%MEAS


*FRAME   WIRE.RIGHT	 	0.3	5	0	0	0	0  1 %IF MADX--> need to compute from CCS to wire.
*FRAME   WIRE.RIGHT.DOF	0	0	0    0    0    0   1  	 TX	TZ	RX	RZ
*POIN
A-TAP.WPS2 	0	-6.035	0  %no sag in this simulation
TAP.A.WPS	0	-4.035	0
TAP.L.WPS	0	3.965	0
B-TAP.WPS2	0	5.965	0
*OBSXYZ
A-TAP.WPS2 	0	-6.035	0	0.0001		0.0001 		10000
TAP.A.WPS	0	-4.035	0	0.0001		0.0001 		10000
TAP.L.WPS	0	3.965	0	0.0001		0.0001 		10000
B-TAP.WPS2	0	5.965	0	0.0001		0.0001 		10000
*FRAME   WIRE.RIGHT.SCALE	0	0	0    0    0    0   1 	SCL
*OBSXYZ
A-TAP.WPS2 	0	-6.035	0	10000 	10000 	0.0001
TAP.A.WPS	0	-4.035	0	10000 	10000 	0.0001
TAP.L.WPS	0	3.965	0	10000 	10000 	0.0001
B-TAP.WPS2	0	5.965	0	10000 	10000 	0.0001
*ENDFRAME
*ENDFRAME
*ENDFRAME

*FRAME   WIRE.LEFT	 	-0.3	5	0	0	0	0  1
*FRAME   WIRE.LEFT.DOF	0	0	0    0    0    0   1  	TX	TZ	RX	RZ
*POIN
A-TAP.WPS1 	0	-6.035	0
TAP.D.WPS	0	-4.035	0
TAP.Q.WPS	0	3.965	0
B-TAP.WPS1	0	5.965	0
