% Description Table 1
*FRAME A-TAP.THEO 0 -1 2 0 0 0 1 		%Theoretical frame of the plate A-TAP
*FRAME A-TAP.REAL 0 0 0 0 0 0 1   TZ	%Real measured frame of the plate A-TAP, TZ freed for the Distance measurement
*CALA 
A-TAP.REF 0 0 0
*FRAME A-TAP.HLS1 -0.3 0 0.5 0 200 0 1
