*ENDFRAME
*FRAME A-TAP.WPS2 0.3 0 0.4 0 0 0 1
*OBSXYZ
A-TAP.WPS2 0    -0.035 -0.0345	0.03	15	0.03		%MEAS
*ENDFRAME
*ENDFRAME
*ENDFRAME

